[Result "0-1"]
[SetUp "1"]
[FEN "r6k/3qb1pp/8/1p6/p1bPpP2/4B3/1PQ4P/R4RK1 w - - 0 24"]
[PlyCount "26"]
[GameId "2130463734561911"]

24. Rf2 Bd3 25. Qd2 b4 26. Kh1 b3 (26... a3 27. bxa3 bxa3 {is also good.}) 27. Rg2 Qb7 28. f5 {Kingside or queenside? Where did Spielmann decide to play?} a3 29. f6 Bxf6 30. Rxa3 Rxa3 31. bxa3 {[%csl Bc2][%cal Gb3b2,Gb2b1,Gd3c2]} Bc2 $19 32. Rg1 Qc8 33. a4 $6 (33. Qb4 h6 34. Qb5 Kh7 {∓ was a must.}) 33... Qf5 34. a5 Qf3+ 35. Rg2 h5 $1 36. Kg1 (36. a6 Qf1+ 37. Rg1 Qxa6 {-+ .}) 36... b2 $1 {[%csl Rb1][%cal Gb2b1]} 0-1

[Event "The Strategy Instructors Volume 3: The Exchange Sacrifice"]
