23... e6 {In the game, Bent Larsen played 23...e5 . What do you play if Black tries to block the diagonal with 23...e6 ?} 24. gxf7+ Kxf7 25. Bxg7 Kxg7 {There is not a single piece to protect the king.} 26. Rg1+ Kh7 ({If} 26... Kf7 $4 {then} 27. Qh6 {creates a mating net.}) 27. Bxe6 {" Such attacks will play by itself. – Ramesh RB "} Rf8 28. Qg2 $18 {[%cal Ge6f5]} *

[Event "The Strategy Instructors Volume 3: The Exchange Sacrifice"]
