1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 d6 6. Bc4 Bd7 7. Bb3 g6 8. f3 Na5 9. Bg5 Bg7 10. Qd2 h6 11. Be3 Rc8 12. O-O-O Nc4 13. Qe2 Nxe3 14. Qxe3 O-O 15. g4 Qa5 16. h4 e6 17. Nde2 Rc6 18. g5 hxg5 19. hxg5 Nh5 20. f4 Rfc8 21. Kb1 Qb6 22. Qf3 Rc5 23. Qd3 Bxc3 24. Nxc3 Nxf4 25. Qf3 Nh5 {The decision you need to make here should be easy for you.} 26. Rxh5 $1 {A 'reflection' of the previous example!} gxh5 27. Qxh5 Kf8 {Black tries to escape.} 28. Qh8+ Ke7 29. Qf6+ Ke8 30. Rh1 $18 {[%csl Rh8][%cal Gh1h8] Rh8+ next wins.} *

[Event "The Strategy Instructors Volume 3: The Exchange Sacrifice"]
