[GameId "2130463734926479"]

27... Be8 {Gligorić played ...Be8 instead of the ...Kf8 we saw previously. How did the game continue?} 28. Qh6 (28. Rh1 {was also strong:} Kf8 29. Bxe6 $1 fxe6 30. Qh8+ Ke7 31. Rh7+ Bf7 32. Qf6+ Ke8 33. Qxf7+ Kd8 34. Qf8# {.}) 28... Rxc3 {Black is forced to return the exchange, hoping that this simplification will allow him to survive…} 29. bxc3 (29. Rh1 $2 {fails to} Qd4 30. bxc3 Qg7 {, when Black defends.}) 29... Rxc3 30. g6 $18 {Shattering Black's dreams!} ({Note from a tester: the move order is important as} 30. Rh1 $2 {is not winning} Qd4 31. g6 ({allows Black to equalize If} 31. Qh4 {, White keeps winning chances.}) 31... Rg3 32. Qh7+ Kf8 {.}) 30... fxg6 31. Rh1 Qd4 32. Qh7+ (32. Qh7+ {Black resigned due to} Kf8 33. Rf1+ {+- .}) (32. Bxe6+ Bf7 33. Qh7+ Kf8 34. Qxf7# {was also good .}) 1-0

