[GameId "2130463734967444"]

27. h3 $6 ({The text move preserved the advantage, but} 27. Bb2 $1 {is killing:} Kh7 28. Qd4 Rg8 29. Re5 Rad8 30. Bd5 {+- .}) 27... Qf5 {Smyslov's bishop is under attack. How did the game continue?} 28. Bc3 Kh7 29. g4 $1 Qg5 30. f4 Qh4 31. Kg2 $1 ({It is too early for} 31. f5 $2 Rae8 32. Qf2 Qxh3 33. Rxe8 {(( 33.fxg6+ is an interessant alternative 33...fxg6 34.Rxe8 Qxg4+= ))} Qxg4+ 34. Kf1 Qh3+ {.}) 31... Rg8 32. Qe7 $1 {Simple and effective. The endgame is winning for White, as Black loses his bishop.} Qxe7 33. Rxe7 Rae8 34. Rxe8 Rxe8 35. f5 {Game over...} a6 36. Kf3 Rc8 37. Bd4 b5 38. Bd3 Rc1 39. fxg6+ fxg6 40. h4 $1 Rd1 41. Ke2 Rh1 42. h5 Rh2+ 43. Bf2 Kg7 44. hxg6 h5 45. gxh5 Rxh5 46. Bd4+ Kg8 47. Be4 a5 48. Kf3 1-0

