[PlyCount "12"]
[GameId "2130463735200931"]

30. Qd2 $6 {With 30.Qd2?!, played in the game, White creates more problems for himself. What is the killer move in this position? Try to find the follow-up as well.} e5 $1 {Allowing the black queen to invade on [h3] with lethal threats.} 31. d5 Qh3 32. Be4 Ng4 {Dancing with the knights...} 33. Nf1 Qxh4 34. Bg2 Ba6 $1 {Eliminating White's best defender - the end is near.} 35. Re1 Bxf1 (35... Bxf1 {White resigned due to} 36. Kxf1 Nh2+ 37. Kg1 Qg5 {, with the triple threat of ...[Qxg2]#, ...[Nf3]+ and ...[Nh3]+. Too many threats for a lonely king…}) 0-1

