15. Ne5 $2 ({White should have focused on defense with} 15. Rg1 f4 16. b3 Bd5 {∞ .}) {What is the best answer to this rather optimistic idea?} 15... Nc6 $1 (15... Rg8 $2 {was played in the game and Black failed to make use of White's bad move.}) 16. Nxc6 Bxc6 17. Rg1 f4 $17 {Black has a strong initiative.} *

