{In this concept there are no fierce attacks but just a pure strategical positional handling of the exchange sacrifice, which includes long-term manoeuvres and domination by pieces. The concept of the exchange sacrifice will be in fully under the microscope in the coming examples. Although not all cases can be examined, we will study a great portion of them and will try to understand the mechanisms. The old masters are for once more the teachers:} 1. Z0 *

