19. Bh4 $2 (19. Bf4 $1 Ng4 20. Bc4 {was the only way for White to stay in the game.}) 19... Ng4 {[%csl Re2][%cal Ge8e2]} (19... Nd4 $2 {was played in the game.}) 20. Bc4 (20. Re1 {was better.}) 20... Ne3 21. Qe2 Re4 $19 {[%csl Rc4][%cal Ge3c4] This seems clear for Black.} *

