24... Ne4 $2 {Unnecessary sophistication!} ({The simple} 24... Bxd4 $1 25. b5 Ba7 26. Bf3 {(26.bxa6? Ne4 27.axb7 Nc3 28.Qc2 Nxd1 29.Qxd1 Qb6 -+)} axb5 27. Qxb5 Ne5 {⩱ would have been good for Black.}) {White could have taken advantage by Black's optimism.} 25. Qe8+ $1 ({After the text move} 25. Nf5 $2 {, White was even losing!}) 25... Nf8 26. Ne6 $1 fxe6 27. dxe6 Nf2+ 28. Kh2 Qxe6 29. Qxe6+ Nxe6 30. Re1 $16 {Editor's Note: This resource, 25.Qe8+ followed by 26.Ne6, is no coincidence – Black shouldn't have exchanged his last rook on move 21!} *

