21... Nb5 ({Probably not the best, although there is no good advice one can give:} 21... Bc5 22. e3 Bxb6 23. Nxb6 {±}) ({and} 21... Be7 22. e3 Ne6 23. Qa4+ Kf8 24. Nd5 {± .}) 22. Qb1 $1 {[%csl Bf5][%cal Gb1f5] The white queen belongs to [f5]!} Qd4 $6 ({Probably a bit better was} 22... Bg7 23. Rd1 Qb8 24. Be4 {± .}) 23. Rd1 Qc5 24. Ne3 {[%csl Bd5][%cal Ge3d5]} ({The text move} 24. e3 {looks very human, just stopping Black's only active idea ...[Nd4] and White slowly starts to improve his position.}) ({But the direct} 24. Ne3 {was just killing!}) 24... Nd4 25. Ned5 Nxe2+ 26. Kf1 $18 *

