{This type of the exchange sacrifice is also quite interesting. One of the sides is placing his/her rook on a strong outpost on an open or semi-open file, in order to avoid exchanging rooks or to gain other important compensating factors; or, finally, to interfere with the opponent's plans. We will start with two examples from the old era:} 1. Z0 *

