20. Qe2 {Material has been restored but Black's weaknesses along the e-file are serious.} Re8 21. Ne6 $1 (21. Be5 $6 e6 22. Qc4 Nd5 {is only slightly better for White.}) 21... Ne4 (21... Bh8 22. Nc7 Rd8 23. Qxe7 {+- .}) 22. Nxg7 Nxg3 $2 {A blunder in a difficult position.} ({Black should have complied with} 22... Kxg7 23. Be5+ Kf7 24. f3 Nf6 25. c4 {± . But of course, his position would be anything but joy…}) 23. Qe5 $1 (23. Qe5 {Black resigned as after} Ne4 24. Nxe8 Qxe8 {,} 25. f3 {is curtains.}) 1-0

