{In the 'Sicilian Defence' we quite often meet the ...[Rxc3] motif. Of course, this motif can either provide positional compensating factors or help to reinforce attacking schemes. In both cases (individual or combined) , it should offer plenty of joy to the sacrificing side.} 1. Z0 *

