14. bxc3 Qc7 15. Ne2 Be7 16. g5 O-O {Black completed his development and looks to transfer his pieces to the attack.} 17. h4 Na4 $1 ({A much better move than} 17... d5 $2 18. h5 dxe4 19. Bxe4 Bxe4 20. fxe4 {⩲ .}) *

