13. Bh4 $6 {Giving up a second pawn cannot be the right policy.} (13. Re1 Nxg5 14. fxg5 Bc6 15. Rg1 e6 {∞}) ({and} 13. Rd4 Nxc3 14. Kd2 Na4 15. Rb4 Nc5 16. Bb5 e6 {∞ , are evaluated as unclear but I prefer Black anyway.}) 13... Nxc3 14. Rd3 Ne4 $1 (14... Nxa2+ 15. Kb2 Nb4 16. Rb3 a5 17. c3 {might allow White to become unnecessarily active.}) *

[Event "The Strategy Instructors Volume 3: The Exchange Sacrifice"]
