{The Strategical Concept The long-term compensation of the double exchange sacrifice is not met often, simply because the invested material is huge. We will start with two games of the 'old era' with a common thread: both of them were played and won by Tigran Petrosian, whose contribution to the exchange sacrifice subject is quite enormous.} 1. Z0 *

