26... Qh4 ({Black didn’t have many options. If} 26... Raa7 {, then} 27. Nf5 Qf8 28. Qf6 {+- , as the coming [Nh6]+ is hard to meet.}) 27. Nxd6 Qg5+ (27... Qe1+ 28. Kg2 Qxe3 29. Bxf7+ Kf8 30. Qh8+ Ke7 31. Nf5+ Kxf7 32. Qg7+ {and [Nxe3] +-.}) ({Or} 27... Raa7 28. Nef5 Qg4+ 29. Kf2 Qh4+ 30. Kf1 Qd4 31. Qxd4 cxd4 32. c5 {+- is a lost cause anyway.}) 28. Kh1 Raa7 (28... Qxe3 {loses to} 29. Bxf7+ Kf8 30. Qh8+ Ke7 31. Nf5+ Kxf7 (31... Kd7 32. Be6+ {+-}) 32. Qg7+ {and [Nxe3].}) 29. Bxf7+ Rxf7 30. Qh8+ $1 {[%cal Yg8h8,Gd6f7]} (30. Qh8+ {, a famous combination! Black resigned, as} Kxh8 31. Nxf7+ Kg7 32. Nxg5 {is too much for him to handle!}) 1-0

