18... Kxf7 $2 {18...h6 was played in the game, but accepting the second sacrifice with 18...Kxf7 leads to disaster anyway. How can you hasten this disaster?} 19. Qc4+ Kg6 20. Qg4+ Kf7 21. Ng5+ $18 {With his last move, Black tried to prevent an eventual [Ng5], but at the same time, created more weaknesses on the light squares around his king.} (21. Ng5+ {A.} Qxg5 {is Black's best move} 22. Bxg5 {.}) (21. Ng5+ {B.} Kg8 {loses the queen after} 22. Qc4+ {, for instance,} Kh8 23. Nf7+ {.}) *

