78. a7 {Editor's Note: In this position, Black is still winning.} Ra8 $1 (78... b3 $2 {was played in the game.}) 79. g5 Rxa7 80. g6 (80. Nd1 Re7+ 81. Kd3 Rd7+ 82. Kc2 b3+) 80... Rd7 $1 (80... b3 $2 81. Nd1 {transposes to the game, with a draw.}) 81. g7 Rxg7 82. Kd3 Rg3 $19 *

