24... Qg4 {The black queen cannot escape.} ({After the alternative} 24... Qc7 25. Bf4 Rhf8 26. Bxc7+ Kxc7 27. Rh4 {, White wins material.}) 25. Rxg4 Bxg4 26. Bxg6 {So, White entered an endgame with an exchange down, but sufficient compensation due to his extra pawns.} Rhg8 27. Bh7 $1 Rh8 (27... Rgf8 {loses to} 28. Bxh6 Rxf6 {(28...Rh8 29.Bf4+ +-)} 29. Bg5 Rf7 30. Bxd8 Rxh7 31. f3 {+- .}) 28. Bd3 $18 *

