23... Bd2 $2 {With the understandable desire to control square [c1].} ({However, instead of this, Black should have tried to create counterplay, since after the game move, White's rook can be transferred on the c-file anyway.} 23... Bxh4 {was the only chance:}) 24. b7 Kf7 25. Rd1 Bh6 26. b3 {Editor's Note: A minor improvement over the game.} (26. Nb4 $6 {An inaccuracy.}) 26... g6 27. g4 Bf4 28. b4 $18 {[%cal Gb4b5] Editor's Note: slightly suboptimal, but a strong human move.} *

