30. Re1 Nf6 ({There is no point in} 30... e4 {, as the [e5]-square cannot be really used.}) 31. Bf1 f4 $1 32. Rce2 ({The other option was} 32. f3 Bf5 33. Rb2 Bg5 34. g4 fxg3 35. hxg3 h5 {, when Black will organise an assault on the white king. Note how the white rooks are just hanging around.}) 32... Bf5 {The correct follow-up.} (32... Rf8 $6 {was played in the game.}) *

