{The passive exchange sacrifice cannot be considered a weapon, but rather a necessity, as we have already explained. So, by definition, it cannot be expected that it will be successful! " Actually, the passive exchange sacrifice should be expected to fail in the end! " And that would be the natural outcome for such a passive concept!} 1. Z0 *

