26... Qxg4+ 27. Rg3 Qd4 $1 28. Rf1 $1 ({Instead,} 28. Rg2 $6 {was passive.}) 28... Qxd5 29. Rd3 Qe6 30. Qd6 $16 {A queen exchange would favor White and if White manages to win either the [e5] or [h6] pawn (or both) , the game will transition into a winning endgame.} *

